editorialNotes.standard: Discover the wonders of the universe with this powerful, easy-to-use astronomy toolkit. Just aim your device to view the real-time positions of planets, stars, constellations, and more in a stunning interactive map. Zoom in to explore Wikipedia articles, 3D models, and other media related to your favorite celestial bodies.

editorialNotes.standard: Learning the ABCs is child's play with this entertaining and educational app. Adorable artwork, colorful creatures, and smooth voice and sound effects enhance an already engaging hands-on experience that makes spelling each and every word an interactive puzzle.

ios.subtitle: Make a routine & put on a show

editorialNotes.standard: Bursting with beats and energy, Toca Dance will make the whole family want to get up and groove. This incredibly cute game puts kids in charge of their own musical productionchoosing dancers, costumes, and techno tracks, and choreographing moves using simple swipes and taps. Once the performance starts, the real fun begins: you can fling items at the stage, set off pyrotechnics and other cool effects, and even cheer (or boo) your squad. Seeing the payoffan awesome video you can sharewill encourage players to jump right back in and start working on their next great show.

Nothing beats a kid-friendly game that keeps the whole family captivatedand Toca has us snipping, straightening, and styling to our heart's content. Once we've perfected our customer's silly new dos, we make sure to add some accessories, snap a pic, and share the hair.

editorialNotes.short: See internal organs in action: lungs breathe, muscles bend and nerves respond to a pinprick.

editorialNotes.standard: Let kids loose in a construction zone where they can place a roof, lay a foundation, paint a house, and more. Children will feel like one of the builders as they operate a crane, cement mixer, and excavator, and theyll delight in all the surprising little interactions with workers in and around the job sites.

editorialNotes.short: Create unique animal species and test their mobility.

editorialNotes.standard: Kids (and kids at heart) can unleash their inner scientists with this captivatingly clever robot-creation kit, which features millions of different combinations for mechanical inventions. Whether youre assembling a wheeled bot with laser guns for arms or a jolly jumping automaton with pogo-stick legs, taking your new bot on a walk through the woods will highlight the successor the rough edgesof your design. While The Robot Factory teaches some nifty physics basics, we like to play around just for the pure fun of it.
editorialNotes.short: Design and experiment with all types of robots.

ios.subtitle: Create to show what you know!

editorialNotes.standard: In this imaginative animated storybook, two of Sesame Streets most popular characters team up to spark your childs love of reading. As fearful Grover concocts hilarious obstacles to keep kids from reaching the last page, eager Elmo asks for their help to discover the mysterious monster at the end of the story. Its an engaging experience that teaches bravery and conflict resolution through lively interactivity, adorable artwork, and heartwarming humor. Parental tips help you integrate these lessons during storytime and beyond, combining learning and play with practical advice from a name you can trust.
